					;any alphanumeric char, or an element that matches any char. the pattern must also be able to match any specific
					;input char (hint: old can no longer be a stringa)
;;see the solution that uses labels - pg 102
(labels ((add10 (x) (+ x 10))
	 (consa (x) (cons 'a x)))
  (consa (add10 13)))




